citeinfo.title: Parcels

descript.abstract: Parcel boundaries are maintained by Ada County Assessor's office. Original basemap data consisted of high accuracy mapping at the center of Ada County where residential and incorporated areas existed. Plats of highways, subdivisions, surveys, and deeds have been added, along with new control and remapping efforts to add to the quality and accuracy of the parcels dataset.
descript.purpose: Used as map layer, analysis, and internet viewing/mapping. The county wide parcel dataset is created twice montly for seamless parcel data viewing on our website.
descript.supplinf: For the most current information call our front desk at 208-287-7262. Or check our website at www.adacountyassessor.org/propsys
